# Place your property images here

This folder is for storing your Moonplace property images.

## Folder Structure (Recommended)

```
public/images/
├── hero/           # Hero section images
├── interior/       # Interior photos
├── bedrooms/       # Bedroom photos
├── outdoor/        # Outdoor/pool photos
├── amenities/      # Amenities photos
├── drone/          # Aerial/drone shots
└── thumbnails/     # Thumbnail versions (optional)
```

## Image Guidelines

- **Format**: JPG or PNG (WebP for better performance)
- **Size**: 
  - Hero images: 1920x1080px or larger
  - Gallery images: 1200x800px
  - Thumbnails: 400x300px
- **File naming**: Use descriptive names (e.g., `living-room-1.jpg`, `pool-view.jpg`)
- **Optimization**: Compress images before uploading (use tinypng.com or similar)

## How to Use Your Images

After adding images here, update the image URLs in:
- `lib/mockData.ts` - Change Unsplash URLs to `/images/your-image.jpg`
- `app/gallery/page.tsx` - Update gallery image URLs

Example:
```javascript
// Before (Unsplash)
url: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-123456'

// After (Local)
url: '/images/interior/living-room-1.jpg'
```
